text: The 2016–17 Slovak Cup (also known as the 2016–17 Slovnaft Cup for sponsorship reasons) is the 48th edition of the competition. The winners of the competition will qualify for the first qualifying round of the 2017–18 UEFA Europa League. ==Participating teams== ===Fortuna Liga (12 Teams)=== {| table width=100% | width=25%
